**组件扫描手动实现**

&nbsp;

**说明：不使用Spring原生框架，自己使用IO+Annotation+反射+集合技术实现**

* **读取类的注解（@Component、@Controller、@Service、@Reponsitory）**
* **将对象注入到IOC容器中**

&nbsp;

![Image](<data:image/jpeg;base64, >)

package com.jack.spring.annotation;

&nbsp;

@Target(ElementType.*TYPE*)\
@Retention(RetentionPolicy.*RUNTIME*)\
public @interface ComponentScan {\
&nbsp; &nbsp; String value() default "";\
}\
&nbsp;

&nbsp;

@ComponentScan(value = "com.jack.spring.component")\
public class SpringConfig {\
}\
&nbsp;

public class SpringApplicationContext {\
&nbsp; &nbsp; private Class\<?\> configClass;\
&nbsp; &nbsp; //ioc存放通过反射创建的对象（基于注解）\
&nbsp; &nbsp; private final ConcurrentHashMap\<String,Object\> ioc =\
&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; new ConcurrentHashMap\<\>();\
\
&nbsp; &nbsp; public SpringApplicationContext(Class\<?\> configClass) {\
&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; this.configClass = configClass;\
&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; //System.out.println("this.configClass" +
this.configClass);\
&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; ComponentScan componentScan =
(ComponentScan)this.configClass.getDeclaredAnnotation(ComponentScan.class);\
&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; String path = componentScan.value();\
&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; ClassLoader classLoader =
SpringApplicationContext.class.getClassLoader();//获得类的加载器\
&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; URL url = classLoader.getResource(path.replace(".",
"/"));\
&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; assert url \!= null;\
&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; File file = new File(url.getFile());\
&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; if(file.isDirectory()){\
&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; for (File f :
Objects.*requireNonNull*(file.listFiles())) {\
&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; {\
&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; String
absolutePath = f.getAbsolutePath();\
&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;
if(absolutePath.endsWith(".class")) {\
&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;
&nbsp; String className =
absolutePath.substring(absolutePath.lastIndexOf("\\\\")+1,
absolutePath.indexOf(".class"));\
&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;
&nbsp; String classFullName = path + "." + className;\
\
&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;
&nbsp; try {\
&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;
&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; Class\<?\> aClass = classLoader.loadClass(classFullName);\
&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;
&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; if(aClass.isAnnotationPresent(Component.class)\|\|\
&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;
&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; aClass.isAnnotationPresent(Controller.class)\|\|\
&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;
&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; aClass.isAnnotationPresent(Repository.class)\|\|\
&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;
&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; aClass.isAnnotationPresent(Service.class)) {\
&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;
&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; Class\<?\> clazz =
Class.*forName*(classFullName);\
&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;
&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;
if(aClass.isAnnotationPresent(Component.class)){\
&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;
&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; Component annotation =
clazz.getAnnotation(Component.class);\
&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;
&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; className =
annotation.value();\
&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;
&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; }else
if(aClass.isAnnotationPresent(Controller.class)){\
&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;
&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; Controller annotation =
clazz.getAnnotation(Controller.class);\
&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;
&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; className =
annotation.value();\
&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;
&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; }else
if(aClass.isAnnotationPresent(Repository.class)){\
&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;
&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; Repository annotation =
clazz.getAnnotation(Repository.class);\
&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;
&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; className =
annotation.value();\
&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;
&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; }else
if(aClass.isAnnotationPresent(Service.class)){\
&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;
&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; Service annotation =
clazz.getAnnotation(Service.class);\
&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;
&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; className =
annotation.value();\
&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;
&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; }\
&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;
&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; ioc.put(className,clazz.newInstance());\
&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;
&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; }\
&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;
&nbsp; } catch (Exception e) {\
&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;
&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; e.printStackTrace();\
&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;
&nbsp; }\
&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; }\
&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; }\
\
&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; }\
&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; }\
\
\
\
&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; }\
&nbsp; &nbsp; public \<T\> T getBean(String Name,Class\<T\> clazz){\
&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; Object o = ioc.get(Name);\
&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; if(\!clazz.isInstance(o)){\
&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; return null;\
&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; }else return (T)o;\
&nbsp; &nbsp; }\
\
&nbsp; &nbsp; @Override\
&nbsp; &nbsp; public String toString() {\
&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; return "SpringApplicationContext{" +\
&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; "configClass=" +
configClass +\
&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; ", ioc=" + ioc +\
&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; '}';\
&nbsp; &nbsp; }\
}
